milestones.description: Flintoff and Strauss's 226-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 170 between Marcus Trescothick and Owais Shah
Flintoff has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (7) in ODIs for ENG, going past David Gower's 5
